"{\"uid\": \"lequipe.fr-Jo-2024-paris-Boxe-Actualites-Le-cio-defend-la-boxeuse-imane-khelif-victime-de-cyberharcelement-et-au-coeur-d-une-polemique-1487667\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Le CIO a hauss\\u00e9 le ton jeudi, pour r\\u00e9agir \\u00e0 la pol\\u00e9mique autour de la participation de la boxeuse Imane Khelif aux Jeux de Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"score\": 0.7310543261139542, \"rank\": 0.3625577342940929, \"text\": \"CIO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q178790\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\"}, {\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hauss\\u00e9 le ton jeudi\", \"from\": 7, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"pour r\\u00e9agir \\u00e0 la pol\\u00e9mique\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"de la participation de la boxeuse\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 97}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ce jeudi, l'instance a publi\\u00e9 un long communiqu\\u00e9 pour apporter son soutien \\u00e0 l'Alg\\u00e9rienne, victime de cyberharc\\u00e8lement ces derni\\u00e8res heures apr\\u00e8s sa victoire express contre l'Italienne Angela Carini.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ce jeudi\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 138}, {\"ngram\": \"l'instance\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"a publi\\u00e9 un long communiqu\\u00e9 pour apporter son soutien \\u00e0 l'Alg\\u00e9rienne, victime de cyberharc\\u00e8lement ces derni\\u00e8res\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00abToute personne a le droit de pratiquer un sport sans discrimination, a expliqu\\u00e9 le CIO dans son communiqu\\u00e9.Tous les athl\\u00e8tes participant au tournoi de boxe des Jeux de Paris respectent les r\\u00e8gles d'\\u00e9ligibilit\\u00e9 et d'inscription \\u00e0 la comp\\u00e9tition, ainsi que toutes les r\\u00e8gles m\\u00e9dicales applicables \\u00e9tablies par l'Unit\\u00e9 de Boxe Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"score\": 0.7310543261139542, \"rank\": 0.3625577342940929, \"text\": \"CIO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q178790\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.658333612711593e-42, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999960900823, \"rank\": 3.9098794716358606e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Toute personne\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"a expliqu\\u00e9\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"Tous les\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"participant\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"ainsi que toutes\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"r\\u00e8gles\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comme pour les comp\\u00e9titions de boxe olympiques pr\\u00e9c\\u00e9dentes, le sexe et l'\\u00e2ge des athl\\u00e8tes sont bas\\u00e9s sur leur passeport.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pour les comp\\u00e9titions\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"le\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"et l'\\u00e2ge des\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"sont bas\\u00e9s sur leur passeport\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00bb Cette r\\u00e9ponse du CIO intervient alors que des voix se sont \\u00e9lev\\u00e9es pour critiquer le potentiel taux de testost\\u00e9rone \\u00e9lev\\u00e9 et la f\\u00e9minit\\u00e9 de deux boxeuses, l'Alg\\u00e9rienne Imane Khelif et la Ta\\u00efwanaise Lin Yu-ting.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e9lev\\u00e9\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"la\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"de deux boxeuses\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"D\\u00e9clar\\u00e9es in\\u00e9ligibles lors des derniers Championnats du monde, elles avaient \\u00e9t\\u00e9autoris\\u00e9es \\u00e0 combattre pour les Jeux Olympiquespar le CIO mardi.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"D\\u00e9clar\\u00e9es in\\u00e9ligibles lors\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"des\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"Championnats\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"monde\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00ab Nous avons eu vent d'informations trompeuses sur deux athl\\u00e8tes f\\u00e9minines (Imane Khelif et Lin Yu-ting) concourant aux Jeux Olympiques de Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nous avons eu vent\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"sur deux\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"f\\u00e9minines\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les deux athl\\u00e8tes participent depuis de nombreuses ann\\u00e9es \\u00e0 des comp\\u00e9titions internationales de boxe dans la cat\\u00e9gorie f\\u00e9minine, notamment aux Jeux Olympiques de Tokyo 2020, aux Championnats du monde de la f\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration internationale de boxe (IBA) et \\u00e0 des tournois approuv\\u00e9s par l'IBA \\u00bb, poursuit le communiqu\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999999890861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9905288301692631, \"rank\": 0.005535319704043136, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Basketball_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Les deux\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"participent depuis de\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"ann\\u00e9es \\u00e0 des comp\\u00e9titions\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"la cat\\u00e9gorie f\\u00e9minine\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"notamment\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"Championnats\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"la f\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration internationale de boxe\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"et \\u00e0 des tournois approuv\\u00e9s par l'IBA \\u00bb\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"poursuit le communiqu\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les fausses informations sur la f\\u00e9minit\\u00e9 de ces boxeuses ont particuli\\u00e8rement circul\\u00e9 ce jeudi, apr\\u00e8s l'abandon express de l'Italienne Angela Carini contre Imane Khelif, dans la cat\\u00e9gorie des moins de 66 kg.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Les\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"informations\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"sur la\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"de ces boxeuses\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1668}, {\"ngram\": \"particuli\\u00e8rement circul\\u00e9 ce jeudi\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"dans\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"la cat\\u00e9gorie\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"des\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"de 66 kg\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"L'Alg\\u00e9rienne, qui compte 37 victoires (dont seulement 5 par K.-O.)\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"L'Alg\\u00e9rienne\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"qui compte\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"37 victoires\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"5 par K.-O.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"pour 9 d\\u00e9faites en carri\\u00e8re, doit disputer son prochain combat samedi contre la Hongroise Anna Luca Hun Hamori (17h22).\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"9 d\\u00e9faites\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"carri\\u00e8re\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"doit disputer son\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"combat samedi contre\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1963}]}]}"